txt.en: You have completed your mission and should talk to to the Dumûri scout.
As you secure sections of the Wrackwade, raise Ambarûli banners to lay claim to them.
The Ordâkhai launched an attack, capturing the floating bridge at Wrackwade. The Dumûri have asked for your help to overcome their defenders and regain possession of the river-crossing.
'It is always a joy to watch you fight. We appreciate what you have done for us this day. Come, let us return to Iridír.'
You have reclaimed the span of the Wrackwade in the name of Ambarûl, and now the Ordâkhai have put forth their champion to challenge you. You should defeat their champion.
'Thank you for your help, [placeholder]! We must never cede control of the Wrackwade to the Ordâkhai.'
